resources.string:
Access Android Phone Through SMS provide additional SMS sending and receiving functionality features. Here You can Remotely Change Profile mode of phone, search contacts, find current location of phone and know about the call log and sms history of your phone. So Write "mm s" for Silent "mm g" for General and "mm v" command for Vibrate mode. Write "cc ali" to search Ali Contact number and vice verse.
Hope you Will Enjoy..
